<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>go the limit • reach the limit</xh5><p> <i>go the limit</i>—<i>(also: go to the limit)</i> 1. do as much as possible: We know that Quiller will <u>go the limit</u> to ensure the success of his mission. 2. go beyond what is reasonable: I am taking my time about it and do not <u>go the limit</u>. Do not let them tell you that I am foolish or hare-brained.</p><p> <i>reach the limit</i>—reach the extreme point: I think those shares have <u>reached the limit</u>, they are not likely to rise higher than they are now.</p> </entry>
